snippet.title: Street Fighter V: Arcade Edition – Lucia Gameplay Trailer | PS4
snippet.description:
Lucia – a detective for the Metro City Police Department who first appeared in Final Fight 3 – makes her high-kicking Street Fighter debut in Street Fighter V: Arcade Edition. It takes a tough cop to police the mean streets of Metro City. Thankfully, Officer Lucia Morgan is able to kick up some heat when needed.

https://store.playstation.com/en-us/product/UP0102-CUSA01200_00-SF5FULLGAME00000
